title: DAZ3D -32265 - Irelia

DAZ3D - 32265 - Irelia - Character and Bikini Set for Genesis 3 Female(s)

Details

Introducing Irelia, a sexy and voluptuous character for Genesis 3 Female and Irelia Bikini for Genesis 3 Female(s).

Irelia comes with detailed skin crafted on the Genesis 3 Base Female UV set and custom sculpted HD Head and Body morphs built from the Genesis 3 Female. Also included is a sexy cleavage morph (using some of the Genesis 3 Female Body Morphs) to add some extra va-va-voom to the bikini! Irelia comes with 7 normal makeups, 7 bolder makeups, 7 matching lip colors and 7 eye colors. Also included are 14 nail colors to coordinate with both the eye makeups and Irelia Bikini textures.

The bikini was designed with Irelia in mind but works with all your favorite Genesis 3 Female shapes thanks to lots of included fits and adjustments. Included are 8 full textures for the bikini with mix and match strap options. Also included are 3 hide options for the bikini bottom straps to customize your look.
